{
  "stem": "3631.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I probably-- I'm sure we knew some, but I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am not aware of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went to high school there, and I was-- I loved geometry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I loved to-- to-- to design the-- the five circles, and squares, and then the different colors, the-- interlock.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I liked this very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, I was not-- never very much sports minded, and I-- so I have no special ideas about this.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I left high school in 1936 with the medium graduation level, and I got a job in a bank.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a private, Jewish-owned bank in the center of town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was an apprentice with a three-year contract from the chamber of commerce.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the way they worked it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I went through every department of the bank-- three months in this, then three months in this department.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- of course, we had no computers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't even-- there was one adding machine in the whole bank that was the head bookkeeper.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even the-- the tellers had no adding machines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was done by hand, and it's good brain training, by-- by the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I worked there until 1938.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The bank was Aryanized, taken over by Germans, by a German bank.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had to leave, like all the other Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I got a job in a depart-- very fine department store in Dresden, mostly exclusively for women and some fine domestics.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It had a fur department.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was very, very fine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I would compare it to Saks Fifth Avenue, but on a much smaller basis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hirsch, H-I-R-S-C-H.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Hirsch and Company.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were in Prager Strasse, P-R-A-G-E-R Strasse, which was the main street that connected the railroad to the-- to the center of town.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
